                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17981024-18-defend181 t17981024-18-punish108"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
